IBADAN â€“ The Fuji music arena was earlier turned into mourning mood with the death of one of its prominent player, Alhaji Isiaka Iyanda Abiodun Sawaba, popularity known as Easy Sawaba. The news was broken through Alhaji Rasheed Ayinde, Fuji Merenge via his social media. Alhaji Ayinde disclosed that Easy Sawaba died at the intensive care unit of the University College Hospital (UCH), Ibadan, after he was reported to have slumped at Iwo Road some days ago. Alhaji erenge however hinted that late Sawaba would be buried today according to Muslim rights at his Oluwo, Egbeda , Ibadan home. It was gathered that the families of the late musician was contacted through his mobile phone when he slumped.